## 📊 Problem #6: Analysis Report Uses Wrong Subset (Only 10 of 30)

### Evidence
The [analysis_report.json](file:///c:/Users/devan/OneDrive/Documents/uptiq/data/results/analysis_report.json) only analyzes 10 queries (the HotpotQA subset from the analysis run), while [run_summary.json](file:///c:/Users/devan/OneDrive/Documents/uptiq/data/results/run_summary.json) shows 30 completed queries. The analysis pipeline is looking for generic filenames (`naive_rag_results.jsonl`, `crag_results.jsonl`) instead of the actual files with the config hash (`*_1775585180.jsonl`).

### Fix
Point the analyzer at the correct files, or standardize filenames.

